# Frontend :

Language.Futhark.Core : 
- Name/VName def
- source code location def + utilities 
Language.Futhark.Primitive :
- Primitive types (scalar types) def
- Primitive values (scalar literals) def
- Basic operations on scalars (both symbolic and in place, for constant folding),
  i.e. unary/binary ops + trig functions etc.

# Backend : 

Futhark.IR.Syntax.Core :
- Basic core IR (types and shapes, small parts of the AST)
- Re-exported by Futhar.IR.Syntax
Futhark.IR.Syntax : 
- Core IR main AST parts (program, function, statement, expression, etc.)
Futhark.IR.Pretty :
- Pretty printing for all the AST


# Utils : 

Futhark.Utils.Pretty :  
- Pretty printing library